description:
Returns the cross-border electricity trading (cbet) in GW between a specified country and its neighbors.


Positive values indicate an import of electricity, whereas negative values show electricity exports.





Response schema:


```json
{
    "unix_seconds": [int],
    "countries": [
        {
        "name": str,
        "data": [float]
        }
    ],
    "deprecated": bool
}
```
